# darwin

Smallest CLI skeleton (Chunk 001).

## Install

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Run

```bash
darwin --help
darwin init
```

`darwin init` creates `chunks/`, `memory/`, `templates/`, and `reports/` in the
current directory. It is safe to run more than once.
